name: Wynn the Wind Medium
desc:
(This card is also always treated as a "Charmer" card.)
You can discard both this card and 1 WIND monster; add 1 WIND monster with 1500 or less DEF from your Deck to your hand, except "Wynn the Wind Medium", also for the rest of this turn, you cannot activate monster effects, except the effect of WIND monsters. When a WIND monster you control is destroyed by battle: You can Special Summon this card from your hand. You can only use each effect of "Wynn the Wind Medium" once per turn.
